fdw_dependencies package
========================

Target: @TARGET_TRIPLE@
Target kind: @TARGET_KIND@

Components
----------

- unixODBC @UNIXODBC_VERSION@ (Linux targets only)
- FreeTDS @FREETDS_VERSION@
- MariaDB Connector/C @MARIADB_VERSION@
- hiredis @HIREDIS_VERSION@
- mongo-c-driver @MONGO_C_DRIVER_VERSION@

This prefix is intended as the reusable client-library dependency package for
building PostgreSQL FDW extensions. It is overlaid on a matching
postgresql_dependencies prefix and reuses that package's common libraries.

It does not include Oracle Instant Client or IBM DB2 CLI/ODBC packages because
those upstream archives have redistribution restrictions; use locally downloaded
vendor archives directly when building an FDW that needs them.
